<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 03 01 00 00 00 09"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />話說最近，<delay20 />我很熱衷於
早起做便當呢！<pageBreak /><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />說到便當中的王者，<delay frames="40" /><anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />果然還是<delay8 />
章魚形狀的香腸對吧？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="001_a" attrib="02 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">沒錯沒錯！</message>
	<message label="001_b" attrib="03 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">不是玉子燒嗎？</message>
	<message label="001_c" attrib="04 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">是飯糰吧！</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="HappyFlower" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我從小時候開始，<delay20 />
就非常喜歡章魚形狀的香腸喔！<pageBreak /><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />它不只是好吃，<delay8 />
還能讓便當看起來更華麗，<delay20 />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />好吃又好看，真是一石二鳥呢！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />玉子燒也很好吃呢！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />光是想起那滋味，<delay20 />
就讓人覺得肚子餓了起來。<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如果在攪拌蛋液時加入牛奶，
就能做出很綿密的玉子燒，<delay20 />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />請你一定要試試看喔，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="TakenAback" target="actor" targetSpec="" />啊啊，<delay20 />我竟然忘記它了！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Confused" target="actor" targetSpec="" />飯糰不僅種類豐富，<delay20 />
而且還能夠當做主菜<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="4" />真聰明！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這麼說來，便當的王者<delay8 />
或許是飯糰呢！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="005" attrib="06 00 00 01 00 00 00 09"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />話說在太陽底下曬乾的衣物……<delay20 />
你不覺得<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />都有股很好聞的味道嗎？</message>
	<message label="006" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="0" arg="0x7 0xb" /></message>
	<message label="007" attrib="65 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />所以我的浴巾<delay20 />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />一定都會<delay8 />每天清洗呢！</message>
	<message label="008" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />把臉埋進剛洗好的浴巾裡磨蹭，<delay8 />
這種幸福感<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />實在是難以言喻呢，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="009" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />雖然洗浴巾還挺累人的，<delay20 />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但是用它擦身體時感覺很舒服，<delay8 />
所以這點辛勞根本就不算什麼！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="010" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那股味道……<delay20 />不知為何
就是能讓人放鬆下來<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />光是想起來，就覺得內心好平靜喔～<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="011" attrib="66 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如果能在好聞的香味中入睡，<delay20 />
感覺睡眠品質應該會滿好的！<pageBreak /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />所以我正在考慮……<delay20 />
下次要不要把我的抱枕
也好好洗一洗呢。</message>
	<message label="012" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如果連床鋪都充滿香味的話，<delay20 />
<anim id="HappyFlower" target="actor" targetSpec="" />感覺一定可以夢到<delay8 />
自己在花園裡散步呢，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="013" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我覺得那個香味一定就是<delay8 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />太陽公公的味道喔～<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="014" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過要洗的東西體積比較大的話，<delay20 />
其實也挺需要體力就是了，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="015" attrib="00 00 00 01 00 00 00 09"><tag a="60" b="0" arg="0x10 0x14" /></message>
	<message label="016" attrib="00 00 03 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />雖然這麼問很突然，<delay20 />不過你覺得<delay8 />
<anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我現在正在想什麼呢？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="016_a" attrib="11 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">小說的事</message>
	<message label="016_b" attrib="12 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">繪本的事</message>
	<message label="016_c" attrib="13 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">詩集的事</message>
	<message label="017" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />沒錯！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />昨天睡前，我讀到一本<delay8 />
非常有趣的小說喔！
<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />是《<tag a="135" b="0" arg="0xcd00" />》的<delay20 />
作者寫的，這是他的第一本小說，<delay20 />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我已經完全成為他的書迷了！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="018" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />沒錯！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我買了一本<delay20 />最近造成話題的<delay8 />
感人繪本，叫做「鬼番茄」。<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />雖然我平常讀的都是大人在看的書，
但看完這本繪本之後，<delay20 />
<anim id="Crying" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我還是感動得大哭了<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="019" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />沒錯！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />其實<delay8 />我將來<delay8 />
想要出一本自己的詩集！<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />雖然我自己默默地寫了很多篇，<delay20 />
<anim id="Hesitate" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但因為太難為情了，<delay8 />
都還沒有給任何人看過呢<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="020" attrib="00 00 03 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />雖然這麼問很突然，<delay20 />不過請問你覺得<delay8 />
<anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我現在正在想什麼呢？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="020_a" attrib="15 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">手套的事</message>
	<message label="020_b" attrib="16 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">襪子的事</message>
	<message label="020_c" attrib="17 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">圍巾的事</message>
	<message label="021" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />沒錯！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就算是洗到縮水的手套，<delay8 />
我也一直很捨不得丟呢。<pageBreak /><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />因為我總覺得手套裡<delay8 />
好像還充滿了<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />許多冬天的回憶<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="022" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />沒錯！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />之前雜誌的特輯上有寫喔<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />「掌握了襪子的人，就掌握了時尚！」<delay20 /><pageBreak /><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如果我也穿上一雙襪子，<delay8 />
是不是就能變成時尚大師了呢？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="023" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />沒錯！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />雖然這是以前的事，<delay20 />
但我曾經<delay8 />花了半年去織一條圍巾喔！<pageBreak /><anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />可是我總覺得
圍著它出門很害羞，<delay20 />
所以連一次都沒有用過<tag a="110" b="0" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今年我一定要鼓起勇氣，<delay20 />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />圍著自己織的圍巾出門去唷，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="024" attrib="19 00 00 01 00 00 00 09"><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />最近<delay8 />我覺得自己的做菜方法
開始有種一成不變的感覺<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我在想，如果多換換作法
會不會更有新鮮感……<delay20 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />所以正在進行各種嘗試呢。</message>
	<message label="025" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="1" arg="0x1a 0x1b 0x1c" /></message>
	<message label="026" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />例如說，幫食譜譜上旋律，<delay20 />
一邊唱歌一邊做菜之類的<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />把食譜的作法配上旋律<delay8 />
會讓印象更深刻，我非常推薦喔。<pageBreak /><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過萬一唱得太投入，
連房子外都聽得到時，<delay20 />
會讓人很害羞就是了，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="027" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />例如說，在做菜時<delay20 />
一邊拍照一邊做之類的<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這樣之後想再修正食譜的時候，<delay20 />
如果有照片，就比較容易回想起來，<delay8 />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />所以我非常推薦喔！<pageBreak /><anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />只是我常常會太投入做菜，<delay20 />
結果照片都拍得
模模糊糊的呢<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="028" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />例如說，一邊做踮腳運動<delay20 />
一邊做菜之類的<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這樣不但可以解決缺乏運動的問題，<delay20 />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />又可以做菜，真是一石二鳥呢。<pageBreak /><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過等料理完成的時候，
腳可能會抽筋，<delay20 />
結果走不動就是了，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="029" attrib="1e 00 00 01 00 00 00 09">老實說，<delay8 />我現在<tag a="110" b="0" /></message>
	<message label="030" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="1" arg="0x1f 0x20 0x21" /></message>
	<message label="031" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />正在想
昨天讀過的小說結尾喔。<pageBreak /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />雖然快樂結局是最理想的，<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但如果故事真的是那樣，<delay20 />
我總有種不太滿足的感覺呢。<pageBreak /><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我該不會<tag a="110" b="0" /><10_4 />
<anim id="Confused" target="actor" targetSpec="" />其實有那麼一點<delay20 />
壞心眼吧<tag a="110" b="0" />？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="032" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />正在想<delay8 />
我開始寫的推理小說喔。<pageBreak /><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如果要把故事寫得很有趣，<delay20 />
那麼主角就必須<delay20 />挺身面對困難，<delay20 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這點我是可以理解<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但我都會把感情投射在主角身上，<delay20 />
實在不忍心給他太多考驗呢，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="033" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />正在想
放在我家<delay8 />郵筒裡的信呢。<pageBreak /><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那封信的外面<delay20 />連寄件者的名字<delay8 />
<anim id="Pardon" target="actor" targetSpec="" />都沒寫呢<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="TakenAback" target="actor" targetSpec="" />難道說，是未來的我寄給自己的信嗎！？<delay frames="40" />
<tag a="110" b="0" /><anim id="Frantic" target="actor" targetSpec="" />光是想像，<delay20 />
我就覺得好興奮喔！
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />所以我還沒打開，就這樣放著了，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="101" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="1" arg="0x8 0x9 0xa" /></message>
	<message label="102" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="1" arg="0xc 0xd 0xe" /></message>
	<message label="034" attrib="00 00 00 01 00 00 00 09"><tag a="60" b="1" arg="0x23 0x24 0x25" /></message>
	<message label="035" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我現在<delay8 />正在做
<tag a="135" b="3" arg="0xcd00" />的玩偶呢～<pageBreak /><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />雖然我想重現那個氣味<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="Sighing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過還是太難了呢，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="036" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我現在<delay20 />非常想讀<delay8 />
關於運動的小說呢。<pageBreak /><anim id="IdeaBulb" target="actor" targetSpec="" />比方說<delay8 />以<tag a="135" b="6" arg="0xcd00" />社團
為舞台的小說之類的！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />青春真美好啊，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="037" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我現在洗衣服的時候<delay8 />
都用<tag a="135" b="1" arg="0xcd00" />香味的洗劑<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Restless" target="actor" targetSpec="" />可是我又想
把<tag a="135" b="1" arg="0xcd01" />香味的洗劑用光<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="IdeaBulb" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不如乾脆<delay8 />混在一起用吧，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="038" attrib="27 00 00 01 00 00 00 09"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我想多學<delay20 />一些特技，<delay8 />
所以請<tag a="110" b="11" arg="0xcd00" />
陪我練習變魔術<tag a="110" b="0" /></message>
	<message label="039" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="039_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">在練習把客人的鈴錢變不見的魔術時，<delay20 />
<anim id="Sighing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我一直說不出
「有人能借我鈴錢嗎？」<tag a="110" b="0" />
<anim id="Restless" target="actor" targetSpec="" />結果當我說不出話<delay8 />顯得不自在時，<delay20 />
那個人<delay8 />就馬上拿出鈴錢借我了。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那人簡直像是有超能力呢。
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我也想變得跟那個人一樣，<delay20 />
<anim id="Assent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />所以我決定接下來要
練習讓湯匙彎曲，<tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="039_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">要是變讓紙箱裡的人消失的魔術時，<delay20 />
<anim id="Shaking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那個人真的消失的話該怎麼辦<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
一想到這我就開始感到不安了。
<anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />結果我就遲遲說不出「請進到紙箱裡」，<delay20 />
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />最後只好把紙箱當成桌子，
開始泡起茶來。</message>
	<message label="039_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">進行猜撲克牌的魔術時，<delay8 />
那個人<delay20 /><anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />說猜中就給我獎品。<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />因為是魔術練習，所以我本應要猜中才行，<delay20 />
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但最後我覺得收獎品有些不好意思，
所以就故意猜錯了，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="040" attrib="29 00 00 01 00 00 00 09"><tag a="110" b="4" />，<delay20 />
你會不時回想起<delay8 />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />剛來到這座島時的事情嗎？</message>
	<message label="041" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="041_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我當時從機場出來的時候，<delay20 />
不知道從哪裡飄來了一股<delay8 />
淡淡的<tag a="110" b="7" arg="0xcd00" />香氣呢<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />所以<delay8 />我每次聞到<tag a="110" b="7" arg="0xcd00" />香氣，<delay8 />
<anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />都會回想起剛來到
這座島時的心情呢，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="041_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我會回想起<delay8 />透過飛機窗戶看見的
<tag a="110" b="33" />的景色呢<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那景色真的十分動人<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我這輩子都不會忘記<delay8 />
當時所看見的景色，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="041_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />當我第一次從機場的大門<delay8 />
走出去的時候，<delay20 />
剛好跟正在抓肚子的<colour id="3" />莫里<colour id="65535" /><anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />對上了眼<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Frantic" target="actor" targetSpec="" />雖然我當下立刻看向其他地方，<delay20 />
不過我到現在都還忘不了<delay8 />
那瞬間的情景，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
</msbt>